item.title: CVE-2023-0447|2023-01-23T16:31:15.592Z -- urkekg -- my%20youtube%20channel
item.description: The My YouTube Channel plugin for WordPress is vulnerable to authorization bypass due to a missing capability check on the clear_all_cache function in versions up to, and including, 3.0.12.1. This makes it possible for authenticated attackers, with subscriber-level permissions and above, to clear the plugin's cache.
